.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-INVOICE-PENDING-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-pending-count \- show invoice counts by status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-pending-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of total, unpaid, and paid invoices.
.PP
Output: JSON object with total, unpaid, paid fields.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list-pending (1),
.BR lightning-node-invoice-stats (1)
